trans-unit.source: Converts instances of <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo> to and from other data types.
trans-unit.target: Konverterer forekomster av <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>til og fra andre datatyper.</xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>

trans-unit.source: This class differs in two ways from <xref:System.ComponentModel.CultureInfoConverter>, the default type converter for the <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo> class.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen, er forskjellig på to måter fra <xref:System.ComponentModel.CultureInfoConverter>, standard typen konverteringsprogram for <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>klasse.</xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo> </xref:System.ComponentModel.CultureInfoConverter>

trans-unit.source: - Uses a string representation based on the <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo.IetfLanguageTag%2A> property rather than the <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo.Name%2A> property (i.e., RFC 3066 rather than RFC 1766).
trans-unit.target: -Bruker en strengrepresentasjon basert på den <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo.IetfLanguageTag%2A>egenskapen i stedet for den <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo.Name%2A>egenskapen (det vil si RFC 3066 stedet RFC 1766).</xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo.Name%2A> </xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo.IetfLanguageTag%2A>

trans-unit.source: - When converting from a string, the properties of the resulting <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo> object depend only on the string and not on user overrides set in Control Panel.
trans-unit.target: -Når konvertering fra en streng, egenskapene for den resulterende <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>objekt avhenger strengen og ikke på brukeren overstyrer angitt i Kontrollpanel.</xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>

trans-unit.source: This makes it possible to create documents the appearance of which do not depend on local settings.
trans-unit.target: Dette gjør det mulig å opprette dokumenter utseendet som ikke avhengige lokale innstillinger.
